---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — joy·object"
  description="I'm joy, a product designer and creative technologist living in Oslo with more than a decade years of experience."
  navActive="about"
>
  <div class="about">
    <!-- Left Column: Header & Nav -->
    <div class="about__left-col">
      <header>
        <a
          href="/"
          class="type-logo home__logo"
          style="text-decoration:none;color:var(--gray-900);"
        >
          joy<span class="home__logo-dot"></span>object
        </a>
      </header>

      <nav class="about__nav">
        <a href="/" class="btn-light">Work</a>
        <a href="/about" class="btn-light is-active">
          About
          <span
            style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:20px;height:20px;"
          >
            <span
              style="width:4px;height:4px;background:var(--gray-900);border-radius:50%;display:block;"
            ></span>
          </span>
        </a>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="about__content">
      <!-- Left: Portrait -->
      <div class="about__portrait-wrap">
        <img
          src="/images/about/joy-portrait.jpg"
          alt="Joy working at desk"
          class="about__portrait"
          width="400"
          height="500"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Text -->
      <div class="about__right">
        <!-- ASCII Art -->
        <div class="about__ascii type-ascii">
          {
            `      ___           ___           ___       ___       ___     
     /\\__\\         /\\  \\         /\\__\\     /\\__\\     /\\  \\    
    /:/  /        /::\\  \\       /:/  /    /:/  /    /::\\  \\   
   /:/__/        /:/\\:\\  \\     /:/  /    /:/  /    /:/\\:\\  \\  
  /::\\  \\ ___   /::\\~\\:\\  \\   /:/  /    /:/  /    /:/  \\:\\  \\ 
 /:/\\:\\  /\\__\\ /:/\\:\\ \\:\\__\\ /:/__/    /:/__/    /:/__/ \\:\\__\\
 \\/__\\:\\/:/  / \\:\\~\\:\\ \\/__/ \\:\\  \\    \\:\\  \\    \\:\\  \\ /:/  /
      \\::/  /   \\:\\ \\:\\__\\    \\:\\  \\    \\:\\  \\    \\:\\  /:/  / 
      /:/  /     \\:\\ \\/__/     \\:\\  \\    \\:\\  \\    \\:\\/:/  /  
     /:/  /       \\:\\__\\        \\:\\__\\    \\:\\__\\    \\::/  /   
     \\/__/         \\/__/         \\/__/     \\/__/     \\/__/    `
          }
        </div>

        <!-- Intro -->
        <p class="about__intro">
          I'm joy, a Danish/Thai living in Oslo. I'm a product designer
          and creative technologist with more than a decade years of experience.
          Lately most of my energy goes into designing AI-native products,
          figuring out how to make generative systems feel intuitive, playful,
          and genuinely useful.
        </p>

        <!-- Body -->
        <div class="about__body">
          <p>
            I'm currently at <a
              href="http://megalearn.se/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener">Megalearn</a
            >
            (the ed-tech startup I co-founded), where I'm leading the design and development
            of a browser-based multiplayer <a
              href="http://megalearn.ai/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener">educational game</a
            >
            powered by generative AI and Three.js. I also work as design lead at
            <a href="http://skalar.no/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Skalar</a
            >, where I designed an AI-driven tool helping small businesses in
            Norway manage their carbon emissions.
          </p>

          <p>
            Before that, I spent 4 years as a senior product designer at
            <a href="http://kahoot.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
              >Kahoot!</a
            >, the game-based learning platform played by over a billion players
            yearly. And before Oslo, while living in Copenhagen, I was a senior
            product designer at Falcon.io (now
            <a href="https://www.brandwatch.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
              >Brandwatch</a
            >), a social media management tool, Graduateland (now
            <a
              href="https://www.jobteaser.com/en"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener">Jobteaser</a
            >), a leading job portal in Europe, and Leo Innovation Lab, a health
            tech incubator. I also spent almost 5 years at <a
              href="https://podio.com/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener">Podio</a
            > designing an online productivity tool, before it was acquired by
            <a href="https://www.citrix.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
              >Citrix</a
            >.
          </p>
          <p>
            I'm a life long learner. My interests are varied, ranging from
            illustration, brain, and cognitive science to AI and creative
            coding. I enjoy building casual games in my spare time since I
            believe games are an excellent medium for people to learn about
            complex systems. As I was trained as an architect, I still work on
            some small residential projects.
          </p>

          <h3
            style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 25px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gray-600); margin-top: 48px; margin-bottom: 16px;"
          >
            Background & Education
          </h3>
          <p>
            Before my career in digital products, I lived in Kyoto as a
            researcher, where I researched Japanese Boy Comics (Shonen manga) at
            Kyoto Seika University. And for many years, I taught at Thammasat
            Design School in Bangkok.
          </p>
          <ul style="list-style: none; padding-left: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">
            <li
              style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 21px; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 8px;"
            >
              M.Sc. Media Technology and Games, IT University of Copenhagen
            </li>
            <li
              style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 21px; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 8px;"
            >
              M.Arch. Architecture and Urban Development, KU Leuven (cum laude)
            </li>
            <li
              style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 21px; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 8px;"
            >
              B.Arch. Architecture, Chulalongkorn University (1st honours)
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Download CV -->
        <div class="about__cv-btn">
          <a
            href="https://www.dropbox.com/scl/fi/yhlreq9gdn46pm3bekvt7/Joy-CV-April-2026.pdf?rlkey=3rotx4qeflz0lju4jf29zzsue&st=koj8bpiu&dl=0"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="btn-dark">Download my CV</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
